## Astro

### SEO (MVP — per PRD § 3.5)

- Set unique `title` and `description` meta tags on every public page
- Add Open Graph tags (`og:title`, `og:description`, `og:image`) for social sharing
- Implement `schema.org` JSON-LD: `LocalBusiness` (bakery) and `Product` (offer items)
- Generate `sitemap.xml` and `robots.txt` at build time
- Use semantic HTML and descriptive `alt` attributes on all images

### Layout and Navigation

- Shared layout: main nav (Home, Offer, About, Orders, Contact), footer with social links, terms, and privacy policy
- Highlight the current page in navigation (`aria-current="page"`)
- Mobile: hamburger menu for navigation on small screens

### Cookie Consent and Analytics

- Show a cookie banner on first visit; remember the user's choice
- Load GA4 and Microsoft Clarity only after consent (`PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID`, `PUBLIC_CLARITY_PROJECT_ID`)
- Declining analytics must not block form submission or browsing

### Analytics Events (MVP)

- `form_started` — user opened the orders page
- `form_submitted` — inquiry submitted successfully
- `cta_clicked` — main call-to-action clicked
